{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">ON HOLD</h2>Unfortunately, due to a myriad of external factors, we have had to put Forging Glory on hold for the time being in favor of smaller titles.<br><br>It's been an amazing, and painstaking, five year journey.  We've learned a lot and experienced wonderful memories we'll cherish forever.  We hope you will continue to join us in our game development adventure by joining us in playing our smaller titles.<br><br>Again, apologies, and thank you all.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/451790/extras/1-12-2020_73234_pm_72_glory1-ccgzh6xx[1].gif?t=1633191366\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">KICKASSERY</h2>Decapitate, dismember, shatter, and mutilate avatars built of light! You're a God of the arena, annihilating all who challenge you.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/451790/extras/Two_Hand_Sword_Knock_Off_and_Brutalize_Less_Tall.gif?t=1633191366\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">MASTERY</h2>Combat is all about skill in Forging Glory.  You must aim your attacks, and your blocks.  There is no magic &quot;block all&quot; button!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/451790/extras/Crossbow_Shot_Less_Tall.gif?t=1633191366\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">CUSTOMIZATION</h2>Create the perfect avatars to fit each battle and play-style using limitless weapons and items.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/451790/extras/Equip_Avatar_Smaller.png?t=1633191366\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FANDOM</h2>Earn glory by pleasing the crowd, leading you to greater rewards and fame!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/451790/extras/Campaign_Map_Scrolling.gif?t=1633191366\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Single-player and multiplayer dynamic campaigns, with 6 game modes.<br></li><li>Fully customizable classless character system<br></li><li>Physics-based combat with 7 unique weapon types<br></li><li>70+ modifiers and 300+ special abilities to mix and match<br></li><li>Build a demon, a humanoid castle, or a blend! Many skins to mix and match, all earned without microtransactions!<br></li><li>Even a fun automatic GIF generator, connected to our Discord, for easy bragging!</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/451790/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1633191366","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/451790/page.bg.jpg?t=1633191366","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/451790/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1633191366","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/451790/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1633191366","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"LAN PvP","id":47},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38},{"description":"LAN Co-op","id":48},{"description":"VR Support","id":31}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">ON HOLD</h2>Unfortunately, due to a myriad of external factors, we have had to put Forging Glory on hold for the time being in favor of smaller titles.<br><br>It's been an amazing, and painstaking, five year journey.  We've learned a lot and experienced wonderful memories we'll cherish forever.  We hope you will continue to join us in our game development adventure by joining us in playing our smaller titles.<br><br>Again, apologies, and thank you all.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/451790/extras/1-12-2020_73234_pm_72_glory1-ccgzh6